-->  What does the dashboard includes ?
1. Total number of employees
2. Attrition count
3. Active Employees
4. Attrition Rate
5. Average Age of employee

--> Visuals Include ...
1. Donut chart to classify gender
2. Bar chart that represents Education wise Attrition
3. Pie chart that represent Department wise Attrition
4. Column chart having Age groups
5. Funnel showing Marital Status of employees
6. Heat Map showing Different Job Roles as per Attrition
7. Slicer to have a dynamic effect
